2026-05-10T19:33:51.7583601Z 240            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-10T19:33:51.7584190Z 241            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-10T19:33:51.7584977Z 242            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-10T19:33:51.7585267Z 243            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-10T19:33:51.7585786Z 244            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-10T19:33:51.7586209Z 245            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-10T19:33:51.7586610Z 246            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
